title: 146: LISTEN TO YOUR HEART: Episode 4 (Boy, Byyeeee)
itunes:title: 146: LISTEN TO YOUR HEART: Episode 4 (Boy, Byyeeee)
description:
Ok Broads, this week’s episode of LTYH picked up so steam again and we didn’t hate it! First The Broads chat Bach Nation tea (aka Peter/Kelley, Hannah Ann, Josh from LTYH, New Bach Series) and then they dive into the last LTYH episode. They discuss the producers thriving this episode, disagree about Julia and Sher Bear, agree about Brandon, EAR MUFFS, vibe hard on some of the performances (not so much on others) and much more! 
*Join us THURSDAY for a great epsiode with Kara Loewentheil of UNF*CK YOUR BRAIN!
